<p>We can offer extra help to people with learning disabilities. For example, we might ask about:</p>
<ul>
<li>the best ways of communicating</li>
<li>likes and dislikes</li>
<li>changing the ward or clinic environment</li>
</ul>

<p>We also have a King's Healthy Passport for people who might need extra help in hospital. We use this to help us understand their needs so we can look after them better. If a patient has filled in a similar passport from a different hospital, we can use that instead.</p>

